{
  "stem": "25639.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "After all, this-- where we were working, that used to be a house at one time, and maybe there is-- is there something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one time-- actually, when we least expected it-- someone from my small group just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that was dangerous for us, because we could be accused of-- of helping her escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And maybe we all could get shot as a result, because lives were cheap.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But what happened was that we could not hear her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Well, we were using shovels, and from the clattering of noise, we could not hear as she fell through a hole into the basement of a bombed-out building.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we looked around, and we-- you know, we couldn't see her anywhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we became very concerned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And suddenly there was a voice coming up from way down under.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "No pun intended for Australia, sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this voice said that 'I am-- I have fallen through a hole into the basement.' And so when we could see that the coast was fairly clear, we yelled down, 'Look around for some food.' And so she did.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And when the right time came-- came again, we whistled down and let her know that we were ready to pull her up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And when we did, her large man's pockets were bulging with black round things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And indeed, they were potatoes, baked and burned from the fire of the bomb.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So we feasted on baked, burned potatoes while on that job, and I can tell you, they were delicious.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- I was not permitted to go down there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I was really everybody's little sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But my job was to look out for the guards, and whistle, and that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I used to whistle pretty well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Not anymore.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
